## ğŸ§ª Features Simulated

- `session_id`: Unique identifier
- `date`: Date of session
- `season`: Holiday period (e.g., "Christmas", "New Year")
- `day_of_week`: (Mon-Sun)
- `time_of_day`: Morning, Afternoon, Evening, Night
- `session_duration`: Minutes spent on site
- `page_views`: Total pages visited
- `device`: Mobile or Desktop
- `bounce`: Whether session was < 1 minute
- `transactions`: Number of gifts purchased (target)

